# 🚀 Quick Start

```bash
# Clone & install
git clone https://github.com/vanashree-ngo/Vanashree-Landing-Page
cd Vanashree-Landing-Page
npm install

# Start everything
turbo dev

# Build the app
turbo build

# Visit:
Web: http://localhost:3000
Docs: http://localhost:3001

# Project Structure
├── apps/
│   ├── web/      # Next.js app
│   └── docs/     # Next.js docs
├── packages/
│   └── ui/       # Shared UI
├── turbo.json




